I installed ubuntu with the help the help of this youtube video..(https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u5QyjHIYwTQ)

The steps were :
1. Installing ubuntu from the ubuntu website->desktop.
2. Formatting the usb.
3. Downloading etcher and flashing the usb.(Luckily for me my friend had the usb with files flashed.)
4. Partioning the available space in windows to get some unallocated space for ubuntu
5. Restart the PC and go to boot manager to boot from the usb.
6. Click on the install ubuntu file in the desktop and follow the instructions
